Modifications
-------------
Mantishack ships the RAPTOR source tree, augmented with mantishack branding
assets (docs/assets/mascot/hero.png, Formula/mantishack.rb,
.claude-plugin/marketplace.json) and a top-level README that identifies this
repository as a fork. The RAPTOR LICENSE, CITATION.cff, CLAUDE.md, agent
prompts, skills, and source files are preserved unmodified relative to the
upstream commit that this fork is based on.
